doc.previous: MTV also welcomed Paris Hilton to its lineup in October 2008 with the launch of her new reality series Paris Hilton s My New BFF 91 In 2009 MTV aired Snoop Dogg s second program with the channel Dogg After Dark and the show College Life based at the University of Wisconsin Madison
doc.after: In late 2009 MTV shifted its focus back to Real World style reality programming with the premiere of Jersey Shore a program that brought high ratings to the channel and also caused controversy due to some of its content 92
